Tom: Hi, Anna. Look! We are at the zoo.
Anna: Wow! I can see a big lion.
Tom: I like the lion. It is big.
Anna: Look! I can see a panda too.
Tom: The panda is black and white.
Anna: I like pandas. They are cute.
Tom: Can you see the monkey?
Anna: Yes! The monkey can jump.
Tom: This zoo is fun. I am happy.
Anna: Me too! Now let us take the MRT.
